  .compute_accuracy
    returns 1.0 for exact match
    returns 0.0 for blank answer
    returns 0.0 for nil answer
    computes near-miss accuracy for typo (runnig)
    computes low accuracy for completely different word (ran vs running)
    is case-insensitive
  .classify_recall
    when incorrect
      returns no_recall for accuracy < 0.7
      returns near_miss for accuracy >= 0.7
      returns no_recall when accuracy is nil
    when correct
      returns automatic_recall for fast response
      returns successful_recall for normal response
      returns effortful_recall for slow response
      returns successful_recall when elapsed_ms is nil
  .compute_rating
    maps no_recall to Again (1)
    maps near_miss to Hard (2)
    maps effortful_recall to Hard (2)
    maps successful_recall to Good (3)
    maps automatic_recall to Easy (4)

