    stops at the first gap
    ignores reviews from other users
  word progress buckets (FT-034)
    counts states with sense_coverage_pct = 0 as zero bucket
    counts states with 0 < sense_coverage_pct < 100 as partial bucket
    counts states with sense_coverage_pct = 100 as full bucket
    returns expected bucket distribution for mixed data
    ignores states belonging to other users
  #daily_reviews
    counts unique cards reviewed today
    counts each card once even with multiple reviews today
    counts multiple distinct cards reviewed today
    excludes reviews from previous days
    ignores reviews from other users
  #daily_goal
    always returns the DAILY_GOAL constant

